38:14.458 --> 38:18.295
<i> And we just sat there</i>
<i> for the whole minute.</i>

38:20.731 --> 38:23.900
<i> There's a lot of slow space.</i>

38:23.902 --> 38:25.902
There's no wasted space.

38:28.106 --> 38:30.006
In.

38:31.843 --> 38:33.910
Out.

38:39.283 --> 38:43.086
<i> I think silence</i>
<i> is one of the greatest gifts</i>

38:43.088 --> 38:44.988
<i> that we have.</i>

38:50.094 --> 38:52.128
<i> His questions are direct,</i>

38:52.130 --> 38:54.264
simple, short,

38:54.266 --> 38:56.166
<i> and then he waits.</i>

38:56.168 --> 38:59.836
<i> He interviewed me,</i>
<i> and he put his face</i>

38:59.838 --> 39:03.206
about three inches away
from my face,

39:03.208 --> 39:06.142
<i> says, "it's so nice</i>

39:06.144 --> 39:09.779
to see you and to be with you."

39:09.781 --> 39:13.116
<i> It scared the living daylights</i>
<i> out of me.</i>

39:13.118 --> 39:17.654
<i> But I realized this is what</i>
<i> children do with adults.</i>

39:17.656 --> 39:19.622
<i> And sometimes after</i>

39:19.624 --> 39:23.293
they answer,
he doesn't say anything else.

39:23.295 --> 39:25.528
So they say a little bit more.

39:25.530 --> 39:28.865
It's-it's a... it's a perfect
interviewing trick.

39:31.470 --> 39:33.136
Very funny. Very funny.

39:33.138 --> 39:34.471
Very funny.

39:34.473 --> 39:36.005
I'm not falling for it.

39:36.007 --> 39:37.774
Very good.

39:47.184 --> 39:51.488
Handyman negri and
officer clemmons, I presume.

39:51.490 --> 39:53.590
Correct as always,
your highness.

39:53.592 --> 39:55.525
<i> Could we take a close look</i>

39:55.527 --> 39:57.660
at, uh, your badge here,
officer clemmons?

39:57.662 --> 40:01.498
My friends, I think,
can read it.

40:01.500 --> 40:04.434
P-o-l-i-c-e.

40:05.403 --> 40:07.103
I have always felt
policemen to be

40:07.105 --> 40:09.506
the most dangerous person
in the neighborhood.

40:09.508 --> 40:12.342
<i> So, to have me playing</i>
<i> a police officer,</i>

40:12.344 --> 40:14.043
<i> I was tremendously hesitant.</i>

40:14.045 --> 40:18.181
<i> But there was something</i>
<i>reluctant about Fred to let go.</i>

40:18.183 --> 40:20.750
<i> And I said, "Mr. Rogers,</i>

40:20.752 --> 40:23.853
"i would be very happy
to be on your program

40:23.855 --> 40:28.124
as long as it doesn't
interfere with my singing."

40:39.037 --> 40:40.770
<i> And he teased me.</i>

40:40.772 --> 40:43.606
