48:11.155 --> 48:14.390
for adults, and so he got
funding to do a show

48:14.392 --> 48:16.759
called <i> old friends...</i>
<i> New friends.</i>

48:16.761 --> 48:20.062
<i> I wonder what it is</i>
<i> that makes one person</i>

48:20.064 --> 48:22.365
<i> push on in the face</i>
<i> of difficulty</i>

48:22.367 --> 48:26.135
<i> and makes someone else crumble</i>
