<i> When it goes to the next level</i>

52:43.628 --> 52:45.294
<i> is in the 1980s when he goes</i>

52:45.296 --> 52:46.428
to the theme weeks.

52:46.430 --> 52:48.030
<i> I mean, to... to do</i>

52:48.032 --> 52:49.298
<i> a week on death...</i>

