I think you are just fine

01:04:09.680 --> 01:04:12.514
exactly the way you are.

01:04:12.516 --> 01:04:13.815
The way I look?

01:04:13.817 --> 01:04:15.217
Yes.

01:04:15.219 --> 01:04:16.685
The way I talk?

01:04:16.687 --> 01:04:18.320
Well, yes.

01:04:18.322 --> 01:04:19.988
The way I love?

